Residents Of Huruma In Nairobi Are Shocked By The Mysterious Death Of A 14?Year?Old Boy Inside Huruma Primary School Compound. According To Residents The Boy Was Playing With Fellow Pupils In The School Playground When The Security Guard Dispersed Them And That Was Last Time The Teen Was Seen Alive. The Police Reports Indicate That The Boy Was Killed By Irate Mob While The Family Are Saying The Boy Was Clobbered To Death By An Unknown Individual.